# Technology Stack for Carcará AI Landing Page

## Core Technologies

### Frontend Framework
@Deno - Modern, secure runtime for JavaScript and TypeScript
- Secure by default with permissions system
- Native TypeScript support without configuration
- Modern JavaScript features without transpilation

@Fresh - Zero-runtime overhead web framework for Deno
- Island architecture for selective hydration
- File-based routing for simplicity
- Server-side rendering for SEO and performance
- No build step required

@Preact - Lightweight React alternative (3KB)
- Compatible with React's API
- Fast alternative to React with smaller bundle size
- Virtual DOM for efficient updates

### UI and Styling
@Tailwind CSS - Utility-first CSS framework
- Rapid UI development with utility classes
- Built-in responsive design system
- Performance optimization with PurgeCSS

### State Management
@Preact Signals - Fine-grained reactivity system
- More efficient than traditional state management
- Automatic dependency tracking
- Minimizes unnecessary re-renders

### Content Management
@deco.cx - Integrated CMS platform
- Headless CMS capabilities
- Content modeling and management
- API-first approach for content delivery
- Built-in deployment pipeline

